products.title: Konya Blackout Tiger Orange
products.description: Konya blackouttiger orange plain roller blind the konya range boasts a huge range of blackout and thermal fabrics to use in any room. The fabric is composed of 100% polyester, with a pvc blackout backing and is rolled around a strong, rust free aluminium tube. products.title: Origin (Blackout) Bright Orange - Roller Blind
products.description: The origin (blackout) range offers the latest in light-blocking window coverings, and the bright orange is no different. But it isn't substance over style here; the bright, eye-catching hue will make a statement wherever its used. The rich, summery glow of the bright orange adds an energised quality and isn't for the shy and retiring. By fixing this blind in the bedroom, you can wake up to this sunshine glow every morning, no matter the weather.

products.description: Our plain blackout fabrics collection feature their most popular blackout colours. Our skylight blinds are ideal for your velux, fakro, rooflite and dakstra windows - all you need to do is choose a design and confirm your window manufacturer and window code (please note that these blinds are not manufactured by velux).
